headline: Williams-Sonoma, Inc. (WSM): A Bull Case Theory
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on Williams-Sonoma, Inc. on M Squared Capital’s Substack by Matthew McClintock. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on WSM. Williams-Sonoma, Inc.’s share was trading at $196.06 as of September 16th. WSM’s trailing and forward P/E were 21.83 and 23.92 respectively according to Yahoo Finance. Comp was above expectations […]
